{"tid":255862,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人真係試過因為運程問題而改過個名?","createTime":"2017-05-24T06:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T08:49:51.000Z","uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10b93a8ac29ad99d3df1dc3682c271ea0b0676c4","tid":255862,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T06:06:37.000Z","msg":"想問下你地係咪覺得自己好運滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者覺得自己本身個名好差而去改?<br />\n<br />\n我咁問係因為無意中發現自己個名改得好一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又比人講中晒啲問題 例如性格人緣精神幾方面咁 <br />\n呢幾年遇親有大事又肯定失敗咁濟<br />\n所以想問下有無巴絲會因為運程算命等等而改過個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分享下"},{"pid":"4eee001a2f6c7e4cbf31cc3caf586fb94c5c7032","tid":255862,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T06:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下你地係咪覺得自己好運滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者覺得自己本身個名好差而去改?<br />\n<br />\n我咁問係因為無意中發現自己個名改得好一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係呢D ON9心理，送錢畀神棍呃<br />\n為左轉運改名，改親多數係生辟字<br />\n<br />\n因為咁你先覺得值"},{"pid":"790ebac5ed976c579d5fce5a7cc7e4cc753b55e2","tid":255862,"uid":104294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T06:37:04.000Z","msg":"風水師講個名麻麻,之後改左名。但改完,覺得一般,冇乜改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a49c8e6f8aeddd8adf5ccb4059fa1ea52aa6d6","tid":255862,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T06:39:13.000Z","msg":"唔好信埋啲咁嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n性格決定命運。"},{"pid":"cca7881b8910f7edb0df39d4e3dea2ac38c52ac5","tid":255862,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:17:54.000Z","msg":"剛剛改完 下星期6拎身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b213fb2a6be8973e91dc71b0dd99d3ffa47b12","tid":255862,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"所有風水命理氣場 不論中西式都好 只係輔助<br />\n唔係話迷唔迷信問題<br />\n八字命格面相係有影響 <br />\n改名只係幫你突破樽頸位, 有一個小小既轉捩點 <br />\n往後點行都係靠你自己 <br />\n叫做係個森林入面比番盞燈仔你摸索個出路<br />\n如果你諗住單靠個名可以乜都唔洗做就好運自然來 咁唔改好過 唔好晒錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1587b78f4f5180a33cee12effdd7b6dcac7196c2","tid":255862,"uid":65893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:23:08.000Z","msg":"風水改名唔一定要改身分證 身邊啲人咁叫你就得"},{"pid":"ce36edf196c2560e6108364a022462a61753d628","tid":255862,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風水改名唔一定要改身分證 身邊啲人咁叫你就得</blockquote><br />\n如果想搞埋財運果PART就最好改埋<br />\n因為有身份證同改名契先改到銀行戶口個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fe280063a4948adce53d46e9c27ed74bef4dac","tid":255862,"uid":65893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:38:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>風水改名唔一定要改身分證 身邊啲人咁叫你就得</blockquote><br />\n如果想搞埋財運果PART就最好改埋<br />\n因為有身份證同改名契先改到銀行戶口個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n改過名好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我兩老都改過 成日都要交一堆文件"},{"pid":"a7fbd7f996a3857a48796bdaa83982d7b1af1d65","tid":255862,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>風水改名唔一定要改身分證 身邊啲人咁叫你就得</blockquote><br />\n如果想搞埋財運果PART就最好改埋<br />\n因為有身份證同改名契先改到銀行戶口個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n改過名好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我兩老都改過 成日都要交一堆文件</blockquote><br />\n其實愈後生改愈好既<br />\n人愈大一定愈多銀行/樓契要搞<br />\n平時去銀行etc改名就係比張改名契+改左名既身份證叫佢改就OK <br />\n法律文件, 樓契呢d就麻煩好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}